OpenSpending,is,a,project,that,seeks,to,track,all,public,government,and,corporate,financial,transactions,made,around,the,world,To,do,so,it,collects,budgetary,data,transactional,data,public,procurement,data,and,other,types,of,data,OpenSpending,currently,offers,hundreds,of,datasets,from,countries,around,the,world,The,project,makes,its,data,available,to,developers,for,use,in,reports,and,data,visualizations,via,REST,API